Requirements
* Eclipse Java EE
* Gradle : (http://www.vogella.com/tutorials/EclipseGradle/article.html#installation-via-the-marketplace)
Help > Install New Software 
Add url : http://download.eclipse.org/releases/neon
Look for :  Gradle

* install android sdk : (http://www.android-dev.fr/integration-du-sdk-android-dans-eclipse#.V6J0heiLTIV)
Help > Install New Software
Add url : https://dl-ssl.google.com/android/eclipse/
Look for <install everything>

** install API 19 and tools 